      "text": "Asia stays ahead of the US in routed share next Wednesday, and Europe stays below one percent.",
      "grade": "correct",
      "note": "Both held. On 10 June Asia stayed comfortably ahead of the US in routed share, and Europe stayed below one percent. It has only widened since."
    }
